Before giving any response, please read this document and confirm to me by saying "Loaded Rules for STEMConnect"

## 1. Description

STEM Communication Web App: Website where STEM can connect to build projects together, collaborate and prepare for exams and study together.

### Features

- Home page: landing page, this is where he will learn what is STEMConnect, trust the company and click on one of the cards (if not registered/login, will ask him to login)
  After login, will redirect to one of those rooms/webpage:
- **Courses** → “Join a course room”: choose course to join the group for chats, video, quizes, meeting, pre-exam study
- Upload note → set price/free → buy/download → rating.
- **Projects** → “Join/Create a project team”: Work on projects with colleagues
- **Tournaments** → “View upcoming competitions”: platform where students can compete in teams for best coding/project (Post a project → recruit teammates → Kanban + standups)

## 2. Tech Stack

| Layer      | Tech                                             |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| Frontend   | React, Tailwind CSS, Socket.io-client            |
