| Database   | MongoDB (Atlas), Mongoose                        |
| Auth       | JWT → OAuth (Google via Passport.js or Firebase) |
| Storage    | AWS S3                                           |
| Testing    | Jest + Supertest (backend), Cypress (frontend)   |
